Export Qualitative Data

Qualitative data can be exported to a .txt file or to the clipboard.

On the Edit menu, select Track Settings. The Track Settings dialog box will open.

Select the qualitative track you wish to export data from.

Select Details. The Qualitative Track Information will open.

Export to File; Select Export to File. In Save in browse to the location you wish to save the file, enter a File name and select Save.

or, Export to Clipboard; Select Export to Clipboard, open an external application (i.e. Excel) and paste the contents of your clipboard.
